installation:

system dependencies:

* sbcl >= 1.0.13 (preferably >= 1.1.0) ccl and clisp should work also nowdays
* cairo
* opengl
* freetype
* glut

lisp dependencies:

* cffi from quicklisp
* metabang-bind from quicklisp
* cl-opengl from quicklisp
* cl-cairo from quicklisp
* infpre from quicklisp
* toolbox from quicklisp
* vektor from quicklisp

after loading: (ql:quickload :perfectstorm)
run (storm:storm)

key/mouse-bindings:
* wasd - scroll
* mouse-wheel or +/- - zoom
* v - toggle shaders
* h - toggle health bars
* ` or ^ - developer console :D
* f - (fake)fullscreen
* esc - quit
